      <title>斯里兰卡将选举总统，国际货币基金组织谈判代表寻求授权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/sri-lanka-to-vote-for-president-as-imf-negotiator-seeks-mandate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡将于 9 月举行选举，选出新总统，现任领导人拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈 (Ranil Wickremesinghe) 寻求获得授权推行严格的财政改革，以使这个南亚国家摆脱有史以来最严重的金融危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/sri-lanka-to-vote-for-president-as-imf-negotiator-seeks-mandate</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 03:15:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩与普京关系促进武器贸易 朝鲜经济反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/north-korea-s-economy-rebounds-as-kim-putin-ties-fuel-arms-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜与俄罗斯的武器转让为金正恩政权提供了支持，朝鲜经济重新复苏，使这位领导人可以在加大对美国和韩国的威胁时避开外交手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/north-korea-s-economy-rebounds-as-kim-putin-ties-fuel-arms-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 03:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰敦促香港阻止俄罗斯绕过制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/ukraine-urges-hong-kong-to-stop-russia-from-bypassing-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两国政府高层官员罕见会晤中，乌克兰外交部长德米特罗·库列巴要求香港特首李家超采取措施，防止俄罗斯及其企业利用香港规避制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/ukraine-urges-hong-kong-to-stop-russia-from-bypassing-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 02:47:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东京通胀加速，日本央行继续考虑加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/tokyo-inflation-quickens-keeping-boj-rate-hike-decision-in-play</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七月份，东京的通货膨胀率连续第三个月加速，为日本央行政策委员会下周开会时可能加息留下空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/tokyo-inflation-quickens-keeping-boj-rate-hike-decision-in-play</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 23:33:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在表情包激增后加入 TikTok</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/vice-president-kamala-harris-joins-tiktok-following-meme-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 正式加入 TikTok，并在这个热门视频分享网站上开设了第一个个人账号，在她宣布竞选总统后，带有她形象的帖子人气飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/vice-president-kamala-harris-joins-tiktok-following-meme-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 22:52:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在哈里斯正式获得提名前不会承诺参加辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/harris-says-she-ll-debate-trump-after-republican-balked-at-host</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在民主党候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯挑战共和党候选人出席先前安排的辩论后，唐纳德·特朗普的竞选团队拒绝承诺与这位候选人进行辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/harris-says-she-ll-debate-trump-after-republican-balked-at-host</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普用封口费给检察官泼冷水，指责他享有豁免权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trump-s-hush-money-conviction-should-stand-manhattan-da-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼哈顿检察官向法官表示，唐纳德·特朗普在 2016 年大选前伪造商业记录，隐瞒向一名色情明星支付的 13 万美元，这纯属个人行为，不受美国最高法院关于总统豁免权的里程碑式裁决的保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/trump-s-hush-money-conviction-should-stand-manhattan-da-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:42:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
